1
00:00:10,181 --> 00:00:11,808
Muraho.

2
00:00:11,808 --> 00:00:14,920
Kandi muhawe ikaze mu isomo ryacu
ryo gutangira ibikorwa bishya!

3
00:00:14,920 --> 00:00:18,984
Ndi Chris Tucci, Umwarimu w'uburyo
bw'ubufatanye n'udushya kuro EPFL

4
00:00:18,984 --> 00:00:20,947
Nkaba nanahagarariye ishuri ryigisha icungamutungo.

5
00:00:20,947 --> 00:00:21,957
Ndi Marc Gruber,

6
00:00:21,957 --> 00:00:24,477
Mwarimu w'ukwihangira imirimo
no Kwamamaza ikoranabuhanga.

7
00:00:24,477 --> 00:00:25,913
Mu kigo kimwe.

8
00:00:25,913 --> 00:00:29,916
Twembi dukorera EPFL,
 Ikigo cy'ubufatanye mu by'ikoranabuhanga cy'Abasuwisi.

9
00:00:29,916 --> 00:00:31,490
Muri Lausanne, Switzeland.

10
00:00:31,490 --> 00:00:34,747
EPFL yibanda
ku kwihangira imirimo n'udushya

11
00:00:34,974 --> 00:00:38,921
Ibi bidufasha kwiga uko twatangira
Ibikorwa binyuranye bishingiye ku ikoranabuhanga.

12
00:00:38,921 --> 00:00:41,978
ndetse no gukorana n'ama kampani
kugirango tuyafashe gutera imbere no gutsinda.

13
00:00:41,978 --> 00:00:46,396
Mu by'ukuri, kuri EPFL, kampani Ebyiri
Buri kwezi zirashingwa.

14
00:00:46,883 --> 00:00:49,279
Chris nanjye twakoze iri somo,
cyane cyane kubera mwebwe.

15
00:00:49,279 --> 00:00:51,420
Hamwe n'ubufasha bw'abadufasha beza cyane

16
00:00:51,420 --> 00:00:53,616
Muzajya mutubona twembi 
muri iri somo

17
00:00:54,117 --> 00:00:56,786
Kandi muzumva byinshi ako kanya
bizavugwa na ba Rwiyemezamirimo.

18
00:00:56,786 --> 00:00:59,254
Baturuka mu bihugu 
binyuranye ku isi.

19
00:01:00,476 --> 00:01:04,005
Ibyigwa by'iri somo
bijyanye n'ubunararibonye bwacu mu bushakashatsi

20
00:01:04,005 --> 00:01:05,576
mu ma kampani arenga ibihumbi icumi 10,000

21
00:01:05,576 --> 00:01:07,302
Baduhaye umusingi ufatika kandi ukomeye

22
00:01:07,302 --> 00:01:10,795
ya buri kazi kakozwe, ibikoresho bakoresheje,
n'ibindi twajyaho impaka.

23
00:01:10,862 --> 00:01:13,706
Ariko igitekerezo cyacu ntabwo ari icyo mu magambo gusa.

24
00:01:13,706 --> 00:01:16,796
Byarakozwe kandi
bisuzumirwa ku bantu ba nyabo.

25
00:01:16,796 --> 00:01:18,599
Batangiye amakampani yakoze neza.

26
00:01:18,599 --> 00:01:21,640
Isomo kandi ryubakiye ku bunararibonye bwacu
Mu kwigisha ikiciro cya mbere n'icya kabiri cya kaminuza.

27
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:24,319
N'amashuri ya Kiyobozi
mu gihe kirenze imyaka icumi.

28
00:01:24,508 --> 00:01:26,533
iki ni igihe cya mbere
twabishoboye

29
00:01:26,533 --> 00:01:29,596
Gushyira ibi byigwa
muri iyi mfashanyigisho y'amashusho,

30
00:01:29,596 --> 00:01:32,831
Kandi twishimiye 
Gusangira amasomo namwe.

31
00:01:32,831 --> 00:01:37,169
Kandi isomo ririmo ibintu byinshi bisekeje, kandi tubasezeranyije ko ritazarambirana.

32
00:01:37,618 --> 00:01:40,994
Ni nde, twe? Turambirana?
Nta kurambirana. (Igitwenge)

33
00:01:41,112 --> 00:01:44,575
Iri somo ryateguriwe abantu,
bashaka gutangira ibikorwa bishya,

34
00:01:44,575 --> 00:01:47,937
Cyane cyane abashaka
mu bijyanye n'amahirwe akura.

35
00:01:48,036 --> 00:01:50,120
Ic'ingenzi kuri twe
ni uko ubyumva.

36
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:53,145
Amoko y'imbogamizi ndetse n'amahirwe 
Ba rwiyemezamirimo bahura nabyo.

37
00:01:53,145 --> 00:01:56,092
Ku buryo mu by'ukuri mubona ibinyuranyo
hagati yo gutangira ibikorwa

38
00:01:56,092 --> 00:01:58,324
No kugenzura
 mu ma kampani yamaze gushingwa.

39
00:01:58,802 --> 00:02:00,860
Muri iri somo muziga

40
00:02:00,860 --> 00:02:03,503
Kumenya no gusuzuma
amahirwe y'ubucuruzi,

41
00:02:03,503 --> 00:02:05,752
uko mwakwamamaza ibisubizo byanyu.

42
00:02:05,752 --> 00:02:07,242
Uko mwashaka amafaranga,

43
00:02:07,242 --> 00:02:08,773
Uko mwacunga amafaranga yanyu,

44
00:02:08,773 --> 00:02:11,422
Uko mwatangira
ibikorwa byo gukusanya amafaranga mu matsinda y'abantu.

45
00:02:11,422 --> 00:02:14,574
N'uko wabona inyungu mu by'ubukungu

46
00:02:14,881 --> 00:02:17,349
Niba wishimira 
kwiyemeza imirimo

47
00:02:17,349 --> 00:02:19,160
cyangwa ari ubuto, n'igitekerezo

48
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:21,682
cyangwa waratangiye
urugendo rwo kwiyemeza imirimo,

49
00:02:21,682 --> 00:02:23,425
Iri somo ni iryawe!

50
00:02:35,658 --> 00:02:37,973
Tuzajya dusuzuma imiterere imbere yawe
uko  tuzakomeza iri isomo 

51
00:02:37,973 --> 00:02:40,748
N'amabazwa yacu
ndetse n'ikizamini cya nyuma

52
00:02:40,748 --> 00:02:44,285
Uzakora mu by'ukuri
inyigo ya mbere y'igitekerezo cy'ubucuruzi 

53
00:02:44,515 --> 00:02:46,431
N'uko uzakusanya amafaranga mu bantu banyuranye.

54
00:02:46,431 --> 00:02:48,351
Ariko ibyo nti bihagije,

55
00:02:48,761 --> 00:02:53,835
Abazatsinda neza muri iri somo
bazahabwa ibihembo bingana n'amadolari 2,500.

56
00:02:54,164 --> 00:02:57,245
Kandi ibyo nti bihagije,
iri somo ryose ni iry'ubuntu

57
00:02:57,372 --> 00:02:59,040
Ubuntu?
Ubuntu

58
00:02:59,506 --> 00:03:02,093
Niba wumva wishimiye,
kwiga iri somo

59
00:03:02,093 --> 00:03:03,299
Ushobora kubikora,

60
00:03:03,299 --> 00:03:06,017
kandi tuzishimira kugufasha
ku rugendo rwawe rwo kwihangira imirimo.

61
00:03:06,387 --> 00:03:08,704
Kandi wakwiyandikisha none aha.

62
00:03:10,005 --> 00:03:11,881
Ibi byose byari 
bitunguranye aho biherera.

63
00:03:11,881 --> 00:03:13,135
(Araseka cyane)

64
00:03:13,135 --> 00:03:16,346
Ibyo byari byo, mu by'ukuri
Ibyo ni Byo.
